is well represented in his art at Cairo Jazz Club.\r\n\r\n<strong>Mahmoud Fahmy: Graphic Designer  </strong>\r\nCool and collected Egyptian freelance designer Mahmoud Fathy brought the CJC drawings to life in 2010 and was responsible for the first batch of CJC printed materials including the creative and upbeat series of posters and flyers CJC generated for bands and festivals. Mahmoud studied design at faculty of Fine Arts in Cairo and worked for numerous organizations such as Promo 7 and LOWE Egypt. He currently lives in Berlin and works for worldwide advertising agency DDB. [/cjc_about_section][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About CJC','','inherit','closed','closed','','57-revision-v1','','','2017-02-26 11:42:01','2017-02-26 11:42:01','',57,'http://104.40.211.237/Cairo-Jazz-Club.wp/website/57-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1952,4,'2017-02-26 11:45:55','2017-02-26 11:45:55','','Let Loose ft. A.K','','publish','closed','closed','','let-loose-ft-a-k-2','','','2017-03-01 13:01:23','2017-03-01 13:01:23','',0,'http://104.40.211.237/Cairo-Jazz-Club.wp/website/?post_type=avent&#038;p=1952',0,'avent','',0),(1953,4,'2017-02-26 11:45:32','2017-02-26 11:45:32','','March 01 insta','','inherit','closed','closed','','march-01-insta','','','2017-02-26 11:45:32','2017-02-26 11:45:32','',1952,'http://104.40.211.237/Cairo-Jazz-Club.wp/website/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/March-01-insta.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1954,4,'2017-02-26 11:48:54','2017-02-26 11:48:54','','Radio Acid / Telepoetic / Marc Wahba','','publish','closed','closed','','radio-acid-telepoetic-marc-wahba','','','2017-03-01 13:41:14','2017-03-01 13:41:14','',0,'http://104.40.211.237/Cairo-Jazz-Club.wp/website/?post_type=avent&#038;p=1954',0,'avent','',0),(1955,4,'2017-02-26 11:47:31','2017-02-26 11:47:31','','March 02 insta','','inherit','closed','closed','','march-02-insta','','','2017-02-26 11:47:31','2017-02-26 11:47:31','',1954,'http://104.40.211.237/Cairo-Jazz-Club.wp/website/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/March-